'''斯特伦马'''（[[希腊语|希腊语]]<span>: </span><span lang="grc">στρέμμα</span>, ''strémma''），或称'''希腊亩'''，[[希腊|希腊]]的一个用来表示土地[[面积|面积]]的计量单位，现在该单位的大小等于1[[公顷|迪卡尔]]，即1000[[平方米|平方米]]。为与之前的旧版本区分，该单位现又被称为'''皇家斯特伦马'''。

== 历史 ==
[[古希腊|古希腊]]时期与斯特伦马对应的面积单位是[[希腊引|平方普勒戎]]（平方引），相当于希腊版的[[亩|亩]]。<span style="background-color: rgb(254, 252, 224);">它最初以两牛联套一天的耕地距离来定义</span><ref>{{Citation|last = Pryce|first = Frederick Norman|author2-last = Lang|author2-first = Mabel L.|author3-last = Vickers|author3-first = Michael|display-authors = 1|editor-last = Spawforth|editor-first = Antony|editor2-last = Hornblower|editor2-first = Simon|editor3-last = Eidinow|editor3-first = Esther|display-editors = 0|contribution = measures|contribution-url = https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=bVWcAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA917|title = The Oxford Classical Dictionary, ''4th ed.''|p = 917|location = Oxford|publisher = Oxford University Press|date = 2012|isbn = 978-0-19-954556-8|ref = {{harvid|Pryce|2012}}|accessdate = 2015-07-13|archive-date = 2015-07-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150714153948/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=bVWcAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA917|dead-url = no}}.</ref>，但名义上是边长为100[[希腊尺|希腊尺]]的正方形的面积。该面积也是{{le|希腊式摔跤|Greek wrestling|古希腊摔跤场}}的尺寸。

'''{{le|拜占庭计量体系|Byzantine units|拜占庭斯特伦马}}'''或'''[[摩里亚|摩里亚]]斯特伦马'''根据土地的好坏和时期的不同而不同，但通常在{{Convert|900|-|1900|m2|sp = us|abbr = on}}范围内。<ref>Siriol Davis, "Pylos Regional Archaeological Project, Part VI: administration and settlement in Venetian Navarino", ''Hesperia'', Winter, 2004 [http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0SDG/is_1_73/ai_n13493303/pg_17] {{Wayback|url=http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0SDG/is_1_73/ai_n13493303/pg_17 |date=20150924044005 }}</ref>它最初也被称为“[[希腊引|普勒戎]]”，但最终被表示用简单的拜占庭犁来翻地的动词“斯特伦马”所取代。<ref>Λεξικό της κοινής Νεοελληνικής (Dictionary of Modern Greek), Ινστιτούτο Νεοελληνικών Σπουδών, Θεσσαλονίκη, 1998. </ref>

在希腊语和英语等语言中，[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]计量土地的面积单位“[[杜纳亩|杜纳亩]]”也被称为'''旧斯特伦马'''、'''{{le|土耳其计量体系|Turkish units of measurement|土耳其斯特伦马}}'''或'''{{le|奥斯曼计量体系|Ottoman units of measurement|奥斯曼斯特伦马}}'''，杜纳亩可能源自于这个拜占庭单位。<ref>V.L. Ménage, Review of Speros Vryonis, Jr. ''The decline of medieval Hellenism in Asia Minor and the process of islamization from the eleventh through the fifteenth century'', Berkeley, 1971; in ''Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies'' (University of London) '''36''':3 (1973), pp. 659-661. [http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0041-977X%281973%2936%3A3%3C659%3ATDOMHI%3E2.0.CO%3B2-K at JSTOR (subscription required)]; see also Erich Schilbach, ''Byzantinische Metrologie''.</ref>这个单位的大小也是因地而异的，《现代希腊语辞典》定义其约{{convert|1,270|m2|sp=us|abbr=on}}，<ref>Λεξικό, 1998</ref>但20世纪初，Costas Lapavitsas在{{le|纳乌萨|Naousa, Imathia}}是按1,600 m²来使用的。<ref>Costas Lapavitsas, "Social and Economic Underpinning of Industrial Development: Evidence from Ottoman Macedonia", ''Ηλεκτρονικό Δελτίο Οικονομικής Ιστορίας'' {{cite web|url=http://www.hdoisto.gr/Keimena/Lapavitsas4112005.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-08-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928095353/http://www.hdoisto.gr/Keimena/Lapavitsas4112005.pdf |archivedate=2007-09-28 }}</ref>

